  "response": "Hootsuite offers several pricing plans to accommodate different needs, including a free plan with limited features. Here\u2019s an overview of their pricing as of October 2023:\n\n1. **Free Plan**:  \n   - Cost: $0/month  \n   - Features: Limited to 1 user, 2 social accounts, and basic scheduling tools.\n\n2. **Professional Plan**:  \n   - Cost: $99/month (billed annually) or $129/month (billed monthly)  \n   - Features: Up to 10 social accounts, unlimited scheduling, and advanced analytics.\n\n3. **Team Plan**:  \n   - Cost: $249/month (billed annually) or $329/month (billed monthly)  \n   - Features: Up to 20 social accounts, 3 users, team collaboration tools, and enhanced analytics.\n\n4. **Enterprise Plan**:  \n   - Cost: Custom pricing (contact Hootsuite for a quote)  \n   - Features: Unlimited social accounts, advanced security, custom analytics, and dedicated support.\n\nAdditional features like extra users, social accounts, or integrations may incur additional costs. For the most accurate and up-to-date pricing, visit Hootsuite\u2019s official website or contact their sales team.",
